---
// Solution.astro — What We Enable
---
<section class="section bg-radial-blue" id="product">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">✦ What We Enable</div>
      <h2>Give compliance teams the evidence required to approve AI systems.</h2>
      <p>Causality provides the forensic visibility, incident traceability, and audit-ready evidence required to safely operate agentic AI in regulated environments.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature Matrix -->
    <div class="bento-grid">
      <div class="card bento-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎬</div>
        <h3>Accelerate AI Deployment Approval</h3>
        <p><strong>OpenTelemetry-Native Forensic Tracing</strong> Automatically reconstruct AI decisions and provide the forensic evidence required to confidently approve production deployments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card bento-card">
        <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>Generate Audit-Ready Evidence in Seconds</h3>
        <p><strong>Instant Forensic Reconstruction</strong> Export structured forensic evidence for audits, investigations, and DORA reporting within seconds of an incident.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card bento-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3>Give Risk Teams Continuous Visibility</h3>
        <p><strong>Continuous Governance Monitoring</strong> Monitor AI workflows with anomaly detection and governance mapping aligned to DORA and SR 26-2 requirements.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card bento-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🌐</div>
        <h3>Maintain Full Infrastructure Control</h3>
        <p><strong>Flexible Deployment Architecture</strong> Deploy within hosted, private cloud, VPC, or fully air-gapped environments while retaining ownership of telemetry and forensic data.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card bento-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🛟</div>
        <h3>24/7 Expert Support</h3>
        <p><strong>Always-On Assistance</strong> Get round-the-clock support from our team to navigate challenges, resolve incidents, and keep your AI systems running smoothly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.bento-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
  padding-bottom: 4rem;
}

.bento-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  padding: 2.5rem;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%), var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.bento-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  border-color: var(--color-cyan);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
}

.card-icon {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  width: 60px;
  height: 60px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
}

.bento-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--color-text);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.bento-card p {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}

.bento-card strong {
  color: var(--color-text);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
}
</style>
